wd:Q497 a wikibase:Item ;
	wdt:P37 "Should be doable within Wikidata, but very tricky to get a reasonable result. A query like SELECT * WHERE { ?sbj wdt:P31?/wdt:P279*/wdt:P1269? wd:Q20899 . ?sbj wdt:P580 ?obj . FILTER(ISLITERAL(?obj)) } ORDER BY ?obj LIMIT 1 will return old radio shows that later became podcasts. Trying to clean up Wikidata to add that these shows are podcasts since a certain date (and using this as a filter in the query) is also complicated as it seems very difficult to find info on when these shows became podcasts."@en ;
	p:P37 wds:Q497-ec399557-44b7-5829-9891-d688de404405 .

wds:Q497-ec399557-44b7-5829-9891-d688de404405 a wikibase:Statement,
		wikibase:BestRank ;
	wikibase:rank wikibase:NormalRank ;
	ps:P37 "Should be doable within Wikidata, but very tricky to get a reasonable result. A query like SELECT * WHERE { ?sbj wdt:P31?/wdt:P279*/wdt:P1269? wd:Q20899 . ?sbj wdt:P580 ?obj . FILTER(ISLITERAL(?obj)) } ORDER BY ?obj LIMIT 1 will return old radio shows that later became podcasts. Trying to clean up Wikidata to add that these shows are podcasts since a certain date (and using this as a filter in the query) is also complicated as it seems very difficult to find info on when these shows became podcasts."@en .

